You can register here. In this upcoming webinar we look at the ins and outs of popular trading styles adopted by short-term traders, identifying the pros and cons of each while highlighting the necessary tools of the trade. Join Moneyweb’s Ciaran Ryan and Shaun Murison, senior market analyst for IG Markets SA, as they discuss the below and more. This webinar takes place on Thursday, January 27 at 11h00. You can register here. More on the guest: Shaun Murison
Senior market analyst for IG  Murison has worked in financial markets for 15 years, previously running IG’s Durban branch in South Africa, before moving to Johannesburg. Murison now works as a senior market analyst for IG, providing research and regular market commentary across all forms of media. He is a registered person on the Johannesburg Stock Exchange (JSE) and a certified financial technician (CFTe).